{
  "texts": [
    "Ability of intrusion detection systems to detect and prevent advanced threats in real time is greatly improved by the incorporation of knowledge graphs into the fusion of threat intelligence.",
    "Each of these methods exemplifies a different strategy for intrusion detection, revealing the many options that can be used.",
    "An adaptable and flexible security approach is necessary since best method to use is determined by factors such as the nature of the data being protected, the nature of the threats being faced, and the requirements at hand.",
    "When it comes to finding security flaws in a system, quantum machine learning (QML) is a huge step forward.",
    "The theoretical foundations of quantum computing hold the promise of unprecedented processing power and information security."
  ]
}